trans-unit.source: Defines an application's caching requirements for resources obtained by using <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> objects.
trans-unit.target: 定義應用程式的快取需求取得使用之資源<xref:System.Net.WebRequest>物件。</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Net.Cache.RequestCachePolicy"></xref> class.

trans-unit.source: This constructor initializes the <xref:System.Net.Cache.RequestCachePolicy.Level%2A> property to `level`.
The <xref:System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel> value controls whether caching is enabled, and when the cache can be used.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel>值控制是否啟用快取，而且當快取可用。</xref:System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel>

trans-unit.source: For additional information, see the <xref:System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel> documentation.
A <xref href="System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel"></xref> that specifies the cache behavior for resources obtained using <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> objects.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel"> </xref> ，指定取得使用資源的快取行為<xref:System.Net.WebRequest>物件。</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel"></xref> value specified when this instance was constructed.
trans-unit.target: 取得<xref href="System.Net.Cache.RequestCacheLevel"></xref>建構這個執行個體時指定的值。
